data.description:
Welcome home! 3 bedroom, 2 bath home designed where the builder utilized every inch of space in this House. 
This home boasts of Granite counters, pantry, large island and split floor plan, high ceilings, a large living area, open concept, and vinyl wood plank flooring and carpet combination. (Carpet in the bedroom areas). This kitchen is ready for the master chef, nice and spacious , with plenty of counter space, cabinets, and beautiful granite countertops is a plus.  The large windows throughout the home allows for natural lighting. The utility room is very spacious with a long shelf for laundry needs.  This spacious Owner's suite has a garden tub, separate shower, huge walk-in closet, double vanity with granite and a ceiling fan. This home is located between an Elementary and a Junior High School which is quite the convenience for school age children.  This home will not last long. Landscaping on the front and back is definitely a plus. The property backs up to the park and back gate allows easy and direct access. The wood fence as well as the trees provides the privacy from the park. This home has been kept in mint condition.  Home conveniently located near Ft Cavasos, churches, malls, hospitals, schools, convenience stores and other businesses in the surrounding areas.
